status_effects_elements.description_localised: Leeched characters take damage at the end of their turn. Opponents are healed by the amount of health taken off.

status_effects_elements.name: STATUS_POISONED_NAME
status_effects_elements.description_localised: Poisoned characters take damage at the end of their turn.

status_effects_elements.name: STATUS_AP_DRAIN_NAME
status_effects_elements.description_localised: Characters with AP Drain gain 1 fewer AP each round.

status_effects_elements.name: STATUS_SHRAPNEL_NAME
status_effects_elements.description_localised: Characters with Shrapnel take damage each time they transform.

status_effects_elements.name: STATUS_SLEEP_NAME
status_effects_elements.description_localised: Sleeping characters can’t use the moves they normally have.

status_effects_elements.name: STATUS_BERSERK_NAME
status_effects_elements.description_localised: Characters with Berserk can only use damaging moves.

status_effects_elements.name: STATUS_CONFUSED_NAME
status_effects_elements.description_localised: Confused characters may use the wrong move or target the wrong character.

status_effects_elements.name: STATUS_CONDUCTIVE_NAME
status_effects_elements.description_localised: Conductive characters take damage whenever any Lightning-type attack is used.

status_effects_elements.name: STATUS_GLASS_BONDS_NAME
status_effects_elements.description_localised: Characters with Glass Bonds take damage each time they transform.

status_effects_elements.name: STATUS_PETRIFIED_NAME
status_effects_elements.description_localised: Petrified characters become Earth type and can only use Defend and Raise Shields.

status_effects_elements.name: STATUS_UNITARGET_NAME
status_effects_elements.description_localised: Attacks from characters with Unitarget that normally target a whole team only affect a single target, and attacks that are normally single-target have reduced accuracy.

waterworks.name: MOVE_WATERWORKS_NAME
waterworks.description_localised: Hits everyone on the battlefield except the user.

water_dance.name: MOVE_WATER_DANCE_NAME
water_dance.description_localised: Hits one target. Uses the user’s Speed stat instead of Melee Attack.

water_wall.name: MOVE_WATER_WALL_NAME
water_wall.description_localised: Sacrifice 20% of HP to create a wall that will absorb up to 3 hits for up to 3 turns.

web_wrap.name: MOVE_NAME_WEB_WRAP
web_wrap.description_localised: Gives the target Tape Jam status for 3 turn(s).

status_effects_elements.name: STATUS_TAPE_JAM_NAME
status_effects_elements.description_localised: Characters inflicted with Tape Jam are prevented from switching out their current tape until either Tape Jam is removed, or their tape breaks.

window.name: MOVE_WINDOW_NAME
window.description_localised: Allows Ranged Attacks to hit the target through walls.

status_effects_elements.name: STATUS_WINDOW_NAME
status_effects_elements.description_localised: Walls owned by characters with the Window status no longer block ranged attacks.

wonderful_7.name: MOVE_WONDERFUL_7_NAME
wonderful_7.description_localised: Hits one target. Inflicts a random debuff.

yule_regret_that.name: MOVE_YULE_REGRET_THAT_NAME
yule_regret_that.description_localised: Hits one target. Lands a critical hit if the target has already taken damage this turn.

zoomies.name: MOVE_ZOOMIES_NAME
zoomies.description_localised: Hits one target. Takes priority over other moves.
